From e7c65fca86128f58da5fd08de398252b5492974e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: StanleyYP Wang <StanleyYP.Wang@mediatek.com>
Date: Thu, 12 Mar 2026 12:23:15 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] mtk: mt76: mt7996: fix testmode for QA tool

fixup! mtk: mt76: mt7996: add testmode support
1. fix naming type: tone bw rename to tone freq offset, update testmode PG V2.7.1
2. fix tx spe index unworking issue
3. fix QA tool invalid pp bitmap issue for bw 20/40
4. Do not check the tx length in mt76_testmode_cmd, as the tx_rate_mode will
be set after the tx length is set in the QA tool
Defer the tx length check to mt76_testmode_tx_config_check
5. Add a channel update before starting TX in case tx_antenna is changed
6. Add tx_len_mode to dynamically switch between tx_length & tx_time
configurations

Signed-off-by: StanleyYP Wang <StanleyYP.Wang@mediatek.com>
